channel.title: Site Logo
channel.description:
Hi, I was wondering if anybody could do me a favour and do me a site logo?
I would appreciate it very much.
I would like a simple emblem that people will be able to see and recognise as my site. I would like the main words to be "Check Shove" (with or without a space, whichever looks best) with a slogan underneath saying "I'm all in".
Something simplistic yet effective similar to this: [IMG]http://static.pokerstrategycdn.com/front/images/logo/logo_pscom_en.png[/img]
Thanks very much.
